  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe validator client logs the entire beacon http endpoint including basic auth fields. It should scrub sensitive information when logging.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse v1.2.1-b34a79d\r\nrustc 1.50.0\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nLog lines which print the current beacon endpoint include auth data. For example:\r\n```\r\nINFO Connected to beacon node                endpoint: https://...\r\nERRO Failed to download proposer duties      err: All endpoints failed https://...\r\nWARN Beacon node is not synced               endpoint: https://...\r\netc.\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nThe logs should scrub that information and simply output the URL without basic auth included.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n",
